data.description: This move-in ready home on over 3 acres is waiting for you! Plenty of space to relax with the split-bedroom open floorplan made even more spacious by the vaulted ceilings and tied together with new life-proof luxury vinyl plank.  Kitchen boasts plenty of counter space for preparation and includes built-in microwave, dishwasher, oven and refrigerator. The primary suite with tray ceiling and walk-in closet is sure to please and mornings will be a breeze in the renovated ensuite bathroom with deep vanity drawers, separate shower and whirlpool tub. Home features include on-demand tankless water heater, attached 2-car garage, tons of storage not only in the attic but in the 8 foot high walk-in crawlspace/basement with concrete pad, and fenced backyard. Speaking of the outdoors, between the oversized front porch and 12X16 updated deck, you will have more than enough room for grilling and chilling.  The quiet yet convenient location offers the best of both worlds. Come see this stunner today!
